parameters: L-love you, \n[1]! I'll see you tonight...
See ya, \n[1]. Thanks for helping find the place, I guess.
Bye Mom, bye Dad! Have a good day!
<Welp, that’s one disaster averted. Dad’s none the wiser,
Ashley’s happy and going to keep our secret,
and Mom is back and we're doing more than ever!>
Hey, you made it! I was just about to head inside...
Gary? Yeah he’s a riot. Bit of a grognard nut but he’s
genuinely nice when you get to know him better. He’s the
guy who first introduced me to CoK.
Dammit... I worked really hard on this campaign!
Hey, Ash, it’s alright. I’m sure you can still run the game.
We still have a lot of the pages.
It doesn’t work unless I have the pages organized and in
front of me. Fuck! I guess I’ll have to cancel game night
until I can replace those parts...
No, you won’t have to do that, Ashley.
Go home and start getting ready, I’ll find those pages.
Y-You sure? I mean, I was questioning if you
were really into playing in the first place.
It’s important to you, so it’s important to me.
Alright, bro. I’ll start setting up. If I could get like
five pages back, I could at least run the first game...
Call me when you find them!
Damn things couldn’t have gotten far...
Collect five of the lost pages around town.
<Am I early? Don’t see Ash anywhere...>
Sorry about that, just had to put on -
My phone... I had to grab my phone.
Oh shut up! Let’s go inside.
